item.description:
Known effects of breathwork. Healing we observe in ourselves and in others: physical, psychological, emotional, spiritual. Potential healing effects of breathwork. Bring your experience and ideas.

This also will be a great opportunity to share your experience for those who will attend meetup and introductory session with Christian on Jan 25th.

(We may go to lunch to nearby 'not average Joe' after meetup, who desires)
item.name: Breathwork: Aspects of healing
